  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431720/extras/b9fcfb2e5b46818f48ef0e46932e701c.poster.avif?t=1689096347\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431720/extras/b9fcfb2e5b46818f48ef0e46932e701c.webm?t=1689096347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431720/extras/b9fcfb2e5b46818f48ef0e46932e701c.mp4?t=1689096347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Become a true sea wolf, defeat enemy fleets, and use your cunning to prevail.<br>Immerse yourself in an exciting VR project inspired by classic seabattle arcade games!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431720/extras/a2f2393e4686160c3a3d9ea8c3854c26.poster.avif?t=1689096347\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431720/extras/a2f2393e4686160c3a3d9ea8c3854c26.webm?t=1689096347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431720/extras/a2f2393e4686160c3a3d9ea8c3854c26.mp4?t=1689096347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br><strong>Sea Rivals VR features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Launch torpedoes using a big red button (yes, just like in the movies!)<br></li><li>Complete intense missions<br></li><li>Appreciate the submarine’s interior, based on real ships like the USS PAMPANITO, HMAS OVENS SUBMARINE, and others!<br></li><li>Use periscopes and radar to gain an advantage in battle<br></li><li>Dive underwater to save yourself and your submarine!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431720/extras/b9fcfb2e5b46818f48ef0e46932e701c.poster.avif?t=1689096347\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431720/extras/b9fcfb2e5b46818f48ef0e46932e701c.webm?t=1689096347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431720/extras/b9fcfb2e5b46818f48ef0e46932e701c.mp4?t=1689096347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Become a true sea wolf, defeat enemy fleets, and use your cunning to prevail.<br>Immerse yourself in an exciting VR project inspired by classic seabattle arcade games!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431720/extras/a2f2393e4686160c3a3d9ea8c3854c26.poster.avif?t=1689096347\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431720/extras/a2f2393e4686160c3a3d9ea8c3854c26.webm?t=1689096347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2431720/extras/a2f2393e4686160c3a3d9ea8c3854c26.mp4?t=1689096347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br><strong>Sea Rivals VR features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Launch torpedoes using a big red button (yes, just like in the movies!)<br></li><li>Complete intense missions<br></li><li>Appreciate the submarine’s interior, based on real ships like the USS PAMPANITO, HMAS OVENS SUBMARINE, and others!<br></li><li>Use periscopes and radar to gain an advantage in battle<br></li><li>Dive underwater to save yourself and your submarine!</li></ul>",
